ght="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-crying-light%252Fid302147864%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Crying Light-Antony & The Johnsons']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/the-blue-notebooks.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/bluenotebook.jpg" alt="The Blue Notebooks / Max Richter" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/the-blue-notebooks.php">The Blue Notebooks<br />Max Richter</a></h4><p>響きがとても心地よいピアノの作品です。残響感がたっぷりのとても美しく、そして静かな楽曲がたくさん収録されています。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0001FT2EE?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0001FT2EE" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Blue Notebooks-Max Richter']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-blue-notebooks%252Fid288286069%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Blue Notebooks-Max Richter']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/room-to-expand.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/roomtoexpand.jpg" alt="Room to Expand / Hauschka" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/room-to-expand.php">Room to Expand<br />Hauschka</a></h4><p>親近感の湧く音作りが特徴の作品です。パーカッシヴなピアノのサウンドが聴いている人の心を優しくさせてくれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000KGGHQ0?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-